= Limelight Changelog

== Version 0.5.3

Some bug fixes, new features, and Playbills!
* Image Player tweaks - feature_request - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/141
* Load each production in a separate Ruby instance - feature_request - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/160
* 0.5.0 Limelight application fails to load due to classfile version - bug - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/158
* Y coordinate on floats not working on Windows - bug - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/156
* Open each production in a separate Ruby instance - feature_request - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/157
* spec directory option for generations - feature_request - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/146
* Percentages for minimum width/height - feature_request - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/147
* greedy dimension - feature_request - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/145
* production is not available in the casted method for the root scene - bug - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/152
* Scrollbars get deleted on remove_all - bug - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/151
* add_extension - remove_extension isn't adding all styles - bug - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/150
* Animation is slow within a slideshow - bug - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/149
* Root level styles can not be references - bug - http://limelight.lighthouseapp.com/projects/12073/tickets/140

